---
name: Socialize!
description: IPO'ing in Q3 of 2014
keywords: 'all'
type: Default
documentation: |-
  will pull down Alex's github activity log

  - modify the API_PORT in the ui container to point to the publicly exposed API port (may require Vagrantfile config)*
  - modify the GITHUB_FEED_URL in the etl container to point to the desired github atom feed

  ![diagram](http://www.gliffy.com/go/publish/image/5993606/M.png)
images:
- name: redis_latest
  source: redis:latest
  category: WORKERS
  type: Default
- name: postgres
  source: postgres:latest
  category: API
  type: Default
- name: api
  source: centurylinklabs/socialize-api:latest
  category: API
  type: Default
  ports:
  - host_port: '3001'
    container_port: '3000'
    proto: TCP
  links:
  - service: postgres
    alias: postgres
  - service: errbit
    alias: errbit
- name: etl
  source: centurylinklabs/socialize-etl:latest
  category: WORKERS
  type: Default
  links:
  - service: redis_latest
    alias: redis
  - service: api
    alias: api
  environment:
  - variable: GITHUB_FEED_URL
    value: https://github.com/alexwelch.atom
- name: ui
  source: centurylinklabs/socialize-ui:latest
  category: UI
  type: Default
  ports:
  - host_port: '81'
    container_port: '80'
    proto: TCP
  environment:
  - variable: API_PORT
    value: '3001'
- name: errbit
  source: centurylinklabs/errbit:0.3.0-dev
  category: SUPPORT
  type: Default
  ports:
  - host_port: '8890'
    container_port: '3000'
    proto: TCP
  links:
  - service: mongo
    alias: mongodb
- name: mongo
  source: mongo:2.6
  category: SUPPORT
  type: Default
  volumes:
  - host_path: "/data/db"
    container_path: "/data/db"
